column2: Sunny- little wind- lake very brown
Sunny- little wind- Assumed time was 12:00.
Water very brown- over 5" rain past 2 weeks.
Much rain.  Lake level: very high
More rain.  Lake level: very high
More weeds this year than last- rain last Sunday
Algae floating on top of the water- something new
Sunny today- algal in the water.
We have had a lot of rain.
There is a lot of algae this year-something new.
Particles floating around in the lake- weeds are in bloom
Very warm day.  Sorry it's been so long between times.  Will return here next year and have more time.
Temperature -43 degrees- rainy- cloudy.  Lake looked dirty.
Sunny- lot of weeds. have a nice day!
The lake was like a mirror- sunny.
Sunny- very nice- lots of weeds.
Windy- many weeds- lake clearer this time.  It filtered easily.
Been very windy.  Too windy to boat.  Cloudy- predict rain.  Ice off about a month.  Plants near surface because lake level is down for this time of year.
Rainy and cold ice out a 2weeks earlier
Chara- pondweed- some duckweed present.  Lots of traffic on lake.
Algae growth starting.  Lots of boat traffic.
Busy boat traffic.  Algae growth continues.
Algae blooms now present in middle of the lake.  16 days of high temps above 80 with no rain.
1 inch of rain last night.  Lake weeds are full growth 0-5 ft dense (celery).
Rain the night before.  Water is clear.
Loon on lake.  Starting to get algae blooms.
Loon still here.  Algae blooms and extensive weed growth.
Loon pair- weeds are in full growth- water turning a murky green.
Sunny after a few days of rain.
very hot 90+ degress- lot of boat traffic saw 2 eagles and loon
